# GitHub Models

Use `github-models/<model>` with VoltAgent's model router.

## Quick start

```ts
import { Agent } from "@voltagent/core";

const agent = new Agent({
  name: "github-models-agent",
  instructions: "You are a helpful assistant",
  model: "github-models/ai21-labs/ai21-jamba-1.5-large",
});
```

## Environment variables

- `GITHUB_TOKEN`

## Provider package

`@ai-sdk/openai-compatible`

This provider uses the OpenAI-compatible adapter.

## Default base URL

`https://models.github.ai/inference`

You can override the base URL by setting `GITHUB_MODELS_BASE_URL`.

## Provider docs

- https://docs.github.com/en/github-models
